加用户：useradd <someuser>
加密码：passwd <someuser>
删用户：userdel <someuser>

实际例子：
[root@zhglxt ~]# useradd mydear
[root@zhglxt ~]# passwd mydear
Changing password for user mydear.
New UNIX password:
BAD PASSWORD: it is based on a dictionary word
Retype new UNIX password:
passwd: all authentication tokens updated successfully.
[root@zhglxt ~]# userdel mydear 
